    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A–H. Begonia corallina Carrière. A, Habitat; B–C, Habit; D, Apex of stem, showing rounded silvery spots on leaf surface; E, Base of stem, showing plant branch; F, Staminate flowers; G, Pistillate flowers; H, Fruits. A–B, D–H from Jacques et al. 2058; C, R. Zanatta. Bars: A–C = 20 mm, D, G-H = 5 mm, E = 10 Cm., F = 7 mm." ;
